T02TD2791E:155b-0: @155b // bcom ldan 'das ye shes kyi 'khor lo'i bdag po la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2791E:155b-1: sngags pa yan lag drug rtsi bas drug /'khor lo 'bar ba dri ma med //
T02TD2791E:155b-3: bskal bzangs sangs rgyas brgya phrag bcu //
T02TD2791E:155b-4: lte ba padmo can nyid de //
T02TD2791E:155b-5: de snying rdo rje 'dzin pa yin //
T02TD2791E:155b-6: de yi thugs ni ye shes che //
T02TD2791E:155b-7: gnyis med thig le dkar 'tsher ro //
T02TD2791E:155b-8: aom a'a: hr'i:h'um phata sv'a h'a /
T02TD2791E:155b-9: g-yas dang g-yon lag mgo bo dang ni de bzhin rkang //
T02TD2791E:155b-10: g-yas g-yon rdo rje yan lag bzhi la go rims bzhin //
T02TD2791E:155b-11: zla mdog me dang nam mkha' aindra dang //
T02TD2791E:155b-12: mar me'i dud mdog gnas drug ngag gi bdag nyid bsam //
T02TD2791E:155b-14: ji bzhin ye shes gzug pa yi //
T02TD2791E:155b-15: man ngag gis ni lha bcings la //
T02TD2791E:155b-16: rnal 'byor mu khyud bzlas pa yis //
T02TD2791E:155b-17: dpal phreng gsum gyi sngags ring brjod //
T02TD2791E:155b-18: sna tshogs kha dog can 'od zer //
T02TD2791E:155b-19: de bzhin dkar dang dmar ba nyid //
T02TD2791E:155b-20: spro dang bsdu ba'i sbyor ba yis //
T02TD2791E:155b-21: don gsum rtag tu bsgrub par bya'o //
T02TD2791E:156a-13: rnam dag ye shes thig le las byung bde ba'i rgyun gyis bla ma dang //
T02TD2791E:156a-14: de las kyang 'phros padma 'dzin sku shel ltar rab dang rab tu gang //
T02TD2791E:156a-15: yang des rdzogs sangs rgyas dang nyan thos sras bcas de bzhin 'khor lo yig 'bru nyid //
T02TD2791E:156a-16: mu khyud 'khor lo zag med ro myang byang chub sems rgyun gyis khyab spro //
T02TD2791E:156a-17: de rjes de nyid rim pa yis //
T02TD2791E:156a-18: ye shes 'od gsal phyung bas kyang //
T02TD2791E:156a-19: yid kyi mun pa kun bsal zhing //
T02TD2791E:156a-20: lus can la yang bdar bar bya //
T02TD2791E:156a-21: ji skad bstan pa'i cho ga yis //
T02TD2791E:156a-22: rnal 'byor rgyud dag gyur pa ni //
T02TD2791E:156a-23: dmigs bya dmigs byed dmigs bral ba'i //
T02TD2791E:156a-24: rnam par mi rtog rang skye 'gyur //
T02TD2791E:156a-25: dpal 'khor lo rnam dag gi sgrub thabs rdzogs so//
